{
  "stem": "13851.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of the people from that Nordhausen were killed from bombardment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That evening-- I told you, I went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We saw a lot of people are hit right in the corner of the building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were people where-- which you saw before, were burning like coals because from the bombardment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- the Americans didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, one-- I remember one American soldier was-- he said, he-- and he like from German, like grandparents or what.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, I am ashamed to say I came out from Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He saw what-- what they did to our people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were survived, maybe, a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what-- how many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We start to-- and after that, we saw the Americans coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went and we tored off my uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found there something, a place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was S-- pilots-- you-- pilots' jackets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stripped all the insignia from the pilots-- what it says.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we-- I got a picture of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I showed you that picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We took a picture with my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had those pilots' jackets, because I tore right away, off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't want to have that-- those-- the stripes, so we-- people should see right away where we were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they could tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Looking at us, you could tell where we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the German civilians starting telling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't know anything about that-- what's been done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took-- saw people were marching to work, to working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they-- they knew exactly what that-- but they try-- they trying to tell us that they were not cooperating with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't help them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They didn't know what went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And what happened, a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
